</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="343951D1F93613C5DFBBFAC3216D5BBE" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="626E6515EFA2D063A1556728F9621644" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BD6F65C228FF2EBBD11FE2F45AF43109" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Apparently rare localised to western Panama and Costa Rica in moist hill forest around 1800-2000 m.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="751F7D542F522E2C458D6D4B80E34A2F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="A1578690FA372C037889DD5E5695956C" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">PANAMA.</emphasis>
Chiriqui: Nueva Suissa, 
<emphasis id="C3E69C5BE7705B2CB8F16F24EFF0B2CD" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">T.B. Croat</emphasis>
13504 (MO).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B4C060F39C2243655C48CC43AA09018E" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="761F3ADEFD7949345ED802D0150E1165" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">COSTA RICA.</emphasis>
<emphasis id="B9654F35CC9F74099FD0C97DB9020CC7" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A. Tonduz</emphasis>
11701 (MO). San 
<normalizedToken id="6647EF5846233D68BC5B3EBCB16F4591" originalValue="José">Jose</normalizedToken>
, Cordillera de Talamanca, Copey de Dota, 
<emphasis id="510A932C374D243E4E27E764A025F705" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">M.M. Chavarria</emphasis>
1069 (K, MO).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="66DAE8F9DB722EEF2A549386531D6142" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="notes">
<paragraph id="1154DE82519AE1C9F81E26A59C45C9A7" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CDF04E644F22C564DB0F8821F8AE305C" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">This species is characterised by the long-peduncled, few-flowered cymes of white flowers with broad oblong-ovate, mucronate, mostly scarious inner sepals.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
